You are here: SHARE A VISUALIZATION

Share a visualization with your colleagues by posting to Chatter, getting its unique URL, downloading a screenshot of it, or downloading its filtered data.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience.
Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To view visualizations: 
Click Share.
Click the tab for the sharing method that you want:
Post to Feed posts to Chatter an image and the link to the lens, dashboard, or app.
Get URL provides a unique URL to the asset.
Download gives you options to share a visualization without giving access to it.

If applicable, click Give Access to set the level of sharing access.
Click Done.

NOTE To share a visualization, you must give access to the app that contains it.
title: Sharing Visualizations in Salesforce CRM Analytics
